### Jobs API - Create and Manage Jobs (PRODUCTION)
# ⚠️  WARNING: These requests target the PRODUCTION environment
# Production URL: https://ag-dt-ppl-api.felixtek.cloud/api/v1
# Use with caution - modifications affect live data
#
# This file contains examples for:
# - Creating jobs (async and sync modes)
# - Getting job status and results
# - Listing jobs with filters
# - Cancelling jobs
# - Retrying failed jobs

@baseUrl = https://ag-dt-ppl-api.felixtek.cloud/api/v1
@apiKey = your-production-api-key


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. CREATE JOBS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create Job - PDF Document (Async Mode)
# Submit a new PDF ingestion job with async processing
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "source_type": "upload",
  "source_uri": "/uploads/sample-text.pdf",
  "file_name": "sample-text.pdf",
  "mime_type": "application/pdf",
  "mode": "async",
  "priority": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "source": "production-test",
    "test_case": "pdf-text-extraction"
  }
}

### Create Job - Scanned PDF with OCR
# Submit a job requiring OCR processing for scanned documents
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "source_type": "upload",
  "source_uri": "/uploads/sample-scanned.pdf",
  "file_name": "sample-scanned.pdf",
  "mime_type": "application/pdf",
  "mode": "async",
  "priority": 3,
  "options": {
    "force_ocr": true,
    "ocr_language": "eng"
  },
  "metadata": {
    "source": "production-test",
    "test_case": "pdf-ocr-extraction"
  }
}

### Create Job - Office Document (Word)
# Submit a Word document for processing
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "source_type": "upload",
  "source_uri": "/uploads/sample.docx",
  "file_name": "sample.docx",
  "mime_type": "application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document",
  "mode": "async",
  "priority": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "source": "production-test",
    "test_case": "word-document"
  }
}

### Create Job - Excel Spreadsheet
# Submit an Excel spreadsheet for processing
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "source_type": "upload",
  "source_uri": "/uploads/sample.xlsx",
  "file_name": "sample.xlsx",
  "mime_type": "application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet",
  "mode": "async",
  "priority": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "source": "production-test",
    "test_case": "excel-spreadsheet"
  }
}

### Create Job - Sync Mode (Immediate Processing)
# Submit a job for synchronous processing (waits for completion)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "source_type": "upload",
  "source_uri": "/uploads/sample-text.pdf",
  "file_name": "sample-text.pdf",
  "mime_type": "application/pdf",
  "mode": "sync",
  "priority": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "source": "production-test",
    "test_case": "sync-processing"
  }
}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 2. GET JOB STATUS AND RESULTS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get Job Status
# Retrieve detailed information about a specific job
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Job Result
# Retrieve the processed output of a completed job
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}/result
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 3. LIST JOBS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List Jobs (Default Pagination)
# Get all jobs with default pagination settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### List Jobs with Status Filter (Pending)
# Filter jobs by pending status
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?status=pending&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### List Jobs with Status Filter (Completed)
# Filter jobs by completed status
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?status=completed&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### List Jobs with Date Range Filter
# Filter jobs by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?date_from=2024-01-01&date_to=2024-12-31&limit=50
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### List Jobs with Source Type Filter
# Filter jobs by source type
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?source_type=upload&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### List Jobs with Pagination
# Paginated list of jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?page=1&limit=5
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 4. JOB MANAGEMENT
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Cancel Job
# Cancel a pending or running job
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Retry Failed Job
# Retry a job that has failed or been sent to DLQ
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}/retry
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "force_parser": "azure_ocr",
  "priority": 10
}

###
